# '''*'''Amy C. Cooper - 1846年结婚 (未育子女).
# '''*'''Julia Foster (Hampton) - 1846年结婚 (未育子女), 1846年分居; 并与他人结婚; 在1855年返回Brigham Young的家中, only to leave him bitterly later.
# '''*'''Abigail Harback (Hall) - 1846年结婚 (未育子女), 1846年回到法定的丈夫名下.
# Naamah K. J. Carter (Twiss) - 1846年结婚 (未育子女), obtained cancellation of her {{tsl|en|Sealing (Latter Day Saints)||sealing}} by 1871, anointed to deceased first husband but still included in will.
# '''*'''Nancy Cressy (Walker) - 1846 (未育子女).
