# {{tsl|en|Ann Eliza Young||Ann Eliza Webb}} (Dee) 1868年结婚 (未育子女), 1875年离婚; her story was the basis of Irving Wallace's 1962 biography ''The Twenty-Seventh Wife''  and of {{tsl|en|David Ebershoff||David Ebershoff}}'s forthcoming novel, ''The 19th Wife''
# '''*'''Elizabeth Jones (Lewis, Jones) - 1869年结婚 (未育子女).
